# Forecast engine

Location: app/server/services/forecast/* with comprehensive tests under .../forecast/__tests__.

Core modules:
- ForecastEngine.ts — orchestrator
- DataLoaderService.ts / DataPersisterService.ts — DB ↔ cache boundary
- ModernCacheService.ts — in-memory performant cache for forecast state
- AccountRegisterService.ts — register-specific logic
- ReoccurrenceService.ts — schedule generation and adjustments
- RegisterEntryService.ts — entry operations
- TransferService.ts — inter-register transfers
- LoanCalculatorService.ts — interest calculations and amortization
- DateTimeService.ts + DateTime.ts — date math and edge cases
- HolidayService.ts — holiday-aware behaviors
- reoccurrenceIntervals.ts, types.ts — constants and typing

Testing:
- Unit, integration, and regression tests with snapshot baselines
- A tsx test-runner allows performance and scenario runs (see package.json scripts)

Guidance:
- Favor pure functions and deterministic inputs per test
- Use helpers in __tests__/test-utils.ts for fixtures
- When adding new features (e.g., new account types), update AccountType flags, loader/persister, and service branches. Extend tests accordingly
